==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Milch
<hw>Milch</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[OE. <ets>milche</ets>;
akin to G. <ets>melk</ets>, Icel. <ets>milkr</ets>,
<ets>mj⟦omac⟧lkr</ets>, and to E. <ets>milk</ets>. See
<er>Milk</er>.]</ety>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>1.</sn> <def>Giving milk; -- now applied only to beasts.</def>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Milch</xex> camels.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Gen. xxxii.</au>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Milch</xex> kine.⟦rdquo⟧ <au>Shak.</au>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Tender; pitiful; weeping.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
<rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mild</ent>⟦br⟧
